snippet.title: Scrap Pack 4 trailer - Ludosity & Remar Games
snippet.description:
Download: https://www.remar.se/daniel/scrappack4.php

A video of the Scrap Pack 4 games, which are mostly small concepts, prototypes, competition entries and the like. The music was made by Salkinitzor, NORDLOEF and Robert Nilsson for Violet Metal, the seventh game shown.
